	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>April 19<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. 1850</date>.</p>
				<p>To the <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#59;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Reverend Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Your communication of the <date>7<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date> inst. conveying the<lb/> MS. Of <persName>Mr. Peynado</persName>&#44; in reply to the Address to the Jews by the Synod of<lb/> <placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; was duly received.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The copy of the &#8220;Occident&#44;&#8221; for <date>January</date>&#44; containing<lb/> <persName>Dr. Schlessinger&#39;s</persName> article&#44; came to hand&#44; several months ago.  But<lb/> I only now learn&#44; through your note&#44; for the first time&#44; to whom<lb/> I am indebted for that courtesy.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">As the Address to which these replies are made&#44;<lb/> emanated from the <hi rend="underline">Synod</hi>&#44; it does not become the persons whose<lb/> signatures are affixed to it&#44; merely as authenticating officers&#44; to<lb/> speak for that body&#44; in advance&#44; or on its behalf&#44; without authority.<lb/>  The documents received from you&#44; and any others on the same<lb/> subject&#44; that may be received from any quarter&#44; will be laid<lb/> before the Synod&#44; at its next annual meeting in <date>October</date>&#44;&#8212;when&#44;<lb/> I have no doubt&#44; it will be as gratifying to the body&#44; as it is to<lb/> myself&#44; to welcome these notices of the address in question&#44; and<lb/> to exhibit to the children of <persName>Abraham</persName>&#44; its views on the points<lb/> submitted on the behalf of your people.</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">With great respect&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">I am</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">your obedt. Servt.</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author">John M. Krebs</persName>&#44; Stated Clerk</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">of the Synod of <placeName>New York</placeName>.</p>
		</body>
